living on the upper path.

00:07:54.090 --> 00:07:57.390 align:middle line:84%
Their heads are not
connected to their bodies.

00:07:57.390 --> 00:08:00.360 align:middle line:84%
And what the Hopi
elders say is that these

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:03.570 align:middle line:84%
