know who they are.

00:08:11.310 --> 00:08:14.070 align:middle line:90%
They've lost themselves.

00:08:14.070 --> 00:08:16.260 align:middle line:84%
And if you look
closely at this path,

00:08:16.260 --> 00:08:19.680 align:middle line:84%
