00:08:35.640 --> 00:08:38.760 align:middle line:90%
The path just stops.

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:40.679 align:middle line:84%
But if you look
at the lower path,

00:08:40.679 --> 00:08:43.620 align:middle line:84%
