to deliver the message

00:09:56.850 --> 00:10:00.150 align:middle line:84%
that this map has left for
the people of the Earth.

00:10:00.150 --> 00:10:05.130 align:middle line:84%
And what he said is in 1998,
that we are now living,

00:10:05.130 --> 00:10:09.730 align:middle line:84%
this moment in the map of
time, the point of no return.

00:10:09.730 --> 00:10:11.910 align:middle line:84%
That while in the
past, it's always

00:10:11.910 --> 00:10:15.570 align:middle line:84%
been possible to choose between
the upper and lower path--

00:10:15.570 --> 00:10:17.850 align:middle line:84%
and truthfully, we
can always choose--

00:10:17.850 --> 00:10:22.170 align:middle line:84%
from 1998 on, it becomes much
more difficult to choose.

00:10:22.170 --> 00:10:24.480 align:middle line:84%
So that was the time,
that was the warning, that

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:27.900 align:middle line:84%
was the message that was
delivered to the United Nations

00:10:27.900 --> 00:10:30.850 align:middle line:90%
by the Hopi nation in 1998.

00:10:30.850 --> 00:10:33.455 align:middle line:84%
And to help them know where
they were on this map,

00:10:33.455 --> 00:10:37.560 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to invite you to look
at the image one more time.

00:10:37.560 --> 00:10:40.710 align:middle line:84%
And on the lower
path, what you see

00:10:40.710 --> 00:10:46.830 align:middle line:84%
