This is when the great
wars were being fought.

00:18:58.500 --> 00:19:03.270 align:middle line:10%
This is when the thinking
that was being created of how

00:19:03.270 --> 00:19:05.160 align:middle line:10%
people relate to other people.

00:19:05.160 --> 00:19:07.170 align:middle line:10%
Darwin is telling
us that when he

00:19:07.170 --> 00:19:10.784 align:middle line:10%
saw the ants capture
another colony of ants,

00:19:10.784 --> 00:19:11.700 align:middle line:10%
they didn't kill them.

00:19:11.700 --> 00:19:13.650 align:middle line:84%
They enslaved them
and made them work.

00:19:13.650 --> 00:19:16.209 align:middle line:84%
He said that is a reflection
of the general law.

00:19:16.209 --> 00:19:18.000 align:middle line:84%
Let the strongest live
and the weakest die.

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:21.750 align:middle line:84%
This later became
survival of the fittest.

00:19:21.750 --> 00:19:23.940 align:middle line:84%
Darwin called it survival
of the strongest.

00:19:23.940 --> 00:19:25.570 align:middle line:84%
And he said this
in his own words.

00:19:25.570 --> 00:19:27.150 align:middle line:90%
And I want you to know that.

00:19:27.150 --> 00:19:28.380 align:middle line:90%
So I'm not mincing words.

00:19:28.380 --> 00:19:30.570 align:middle line:90%
Survival of the strongest.

00:19:30.570 --> 00:19:34.770 align:middle line:84%
The ideas of the great genocides
and the great suffering

00:19:34.770 --> 00:19:39.600 align:middle line:84%
of the late 1800s, the 1900s
throughout the 20th century

00:19:39.600 --> 00:19:41.850 align:middle line:84%
are directly linked
to this thinking.

00:19:41.850 --> 00:19:44.370 align:middle line:10%
If you look at the manifestos
and you look at the writings

00:19:44.370 --> 00:19:47.640 align:middle line:10%
and you look at the lengths
of the greatest acts of war,

00:19:47.640 --> 00:19:51.270 align:middle line:10%
aggression, and genocide,
the philosophies

00:19:51.270 --> 00:19:55.080 align:middle line:10%
are directly based
and sometimes quoted.

00:19:55.080 --> 00:19:57.270 align:middle line:10%
I'm not saying
Darwin intended this.

00:19:57.270 --> 00:20:00.120 align:middle line:10%
But this is how a dangerous
thinking like this

00:20:00.120 --> 00:20:03.000 align:middle line:10%
can be misinterpreted
and applied

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:05.760 align:middle line:10%
in horrible ways that
create tremendous suffering

00:20:05.760 --> 00:20:07.000 align:middle line:10%
in our world.

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:09.480 align:middle line:84%
And it's based on
something that's not true.

00:20:09.480 --> 00:20:11.790 align:middle line:84%
This is a false
assumption of science,

00:20:11.790 --> 00:20:13.350 align:middle line:90%
